<div id="pf4438" class="pf w57 h303" data-page-no="4438"><div class="pc pc4438 w57 h303"><div class="t m1872 xc4 hd y2e76 ff3 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 2 July 8-14 </div><div class="t m14b5 x92 hd y9d5 ff3 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;I counsel thee to buy of me&quot; (Rev. </div><div class="t m42b x0 hd y3c9 ff3 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3:18). </div><div class="t m52f x92 h35 ya40 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The wonderful thing about God&apos;s </div><div class="t m8ba x0 h35 y855 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">messages of reproof is that remedies </div><div class="t ma11 x0 h35 ya01 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">are offered. </div><div class="t m333 x15 h35 y8d5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">For many physical ailments that are </div><div class="t ma80 x0 h35 yb0c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">correctly diagnosed by the physician, </div><div class="t m25e x0 h35 y1320 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">there is no known cure. He has to tell </div><div class="t mcb x0 h35 yb0d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the patient, &quot;This is our diagnosis. We </div><div class="t m9df x0 h35 yef5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">are sure about the nature and the </div><div class="t m88f xb7 h35 ydf7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">result of your illness. But, </div><div class="t m71e xb7 h35 y1321 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">unfortunately, we can do nothing to </div><div class="t mdaf xb7 h35 y2de ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">heal you.&quot; </div><div class="t m5fc x15 h35 y126b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Not in the Laodicean case however. </div><div class="t mf37 x0 h35 ydd ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">We may be very happy that the divine </div><div class="t m2ab xb7 h35 ye85 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and merciful Physician has not only </div><div class="t m171 xb7 h35 yf89 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the ability to discover the origin and </div><div class="t m837 xb7 h35 y3a5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the cause of our condition, but He has </div><div class="t m787 xb7 h35 y7b4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">also the absolute capability of </div><div class="t m1a1 xb7 h35 y843 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">effecting a complete healing. And not </div><div class="t m96c xb7 h35 y8d8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">only this, but He offers to us very </div><div class="t m6af xb7 h35 y66 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">graciously the needed medicines that </div><div class="t m4d6 xb7 h35 y8c0 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">in this case are specific and absolute in </div><div class="t m100c xb7 h35 y512 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">their curing effect. </div><div class="t me1b x27 h35 y3dd ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">It would not be fair to </div><div class="t m82f xb7 h35 y477 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">overemphasize the negative part of </div><div class="t m8ff xb7 h35 y706 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the message and fail to give equal </div><div class="t m7a0 xb9 h35 yc57 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">treatment to the most beautiful part of </div><div class="t m17c xb9 h35 y82b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">it: Christ&apos;s generous offer and the </div><div class="t mbe0 xb9 h35 y157b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">absolute certainty that if the needy </div><div class="t m299 xb9 h35 y4f1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">person accepts it and does what the </div><div class="t m6e9 xb9 h35 y7bf ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">counsel calls for, the healing effect is </div><div class="t m12eb xb9 h35 y674 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">totally guaranteed. </div><div class="t m1c5 x27 h35 y78c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">So, in dealing with the positive part </div><div class="t m26d xb9 h35 yf83 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of this great subject, we are dealing in </div><div class="t m6d5 xb9 h35 y1323 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">essence with the heart itself of the </div><div class="t m61e xb9 h35 y344 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Laodicean message. The wonderful </div><div class="t mb1 x3 h35 y7a2 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">subject of the righteousness of Christ </div><div class="t m1176 xb9 h35 y941 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and the possibility of acquiring the </div><div class="t m180 x3 h35 y1325 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">character of Jesus and being made </div><div class="t m58f x3 h35 y3b7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">participants of the divine nature is the  </div><div class="t m170 x20 h35 y15d9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">real issue contained in the message to </div><div class="t m33d x20 h35 y7a5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the Laodiceans. </div><div class="t m88b x21 h35 yaec ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Every child of Adam has ready </div><div class="t m6e9 x58 h35 y4d3 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">accessibility to complete forgiveness </div><div class="t m52f x20 h35 yfb8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and to total victory </div><div class="t m1958 xb5 hd y793 ff3 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">because </div><div class="t m87b xe9 h35 y793 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">he can </div><div class="t mf70 x58 h35 ya68 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">avail himself of Jesus&apos; grace, the only </div><div class="t m6ad x58 h35 y6cd ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">means of salvation. Moreover, any </div><div class="t m272 x58 h35 ya44 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Christian who feels the need of a </div><div class="t mb24 x58 h35 yc54 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">change will enjoy the privilege of </div><div class="t m1be x58 h35 y769 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">having the Holy Spirit work upon his </div><div class="t mb77 x58 h35 y127c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">heart. In other words, the three </div><div class="t m978 x58 h35 y15ed ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">members of the Godhead work </div><div class="t m11f x58 h35 y2dd ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">together to restore every spiritually </div><div class="t ma0 x58 h35 y1976 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ailing child of God, sick of sin, looking </div><div class="t m5ef x58 h35 y2ff ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for deliverance and strength. </div><div class="t mec5 x58 hd y723 ff3 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS </div><div class="t m78a x58 hd y904 ff3 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t me4b x7 hd y85e ff3 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;I counsel thee to buy of me&quot; </div><di